description: This Chainlink VRF common Sakura purrs with a rating of 17, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 34, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Stringalong for East, Box for South, and Box for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10172-77440-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [34 Votes, Common]
